description: The laughingstock of other goblins, who themselves are the laughingstock of everyone else.
The toughest goblin... of a group of the weakest goblins. Possibly a threat, maybe? To a toy poodle?
Bigger than the average human, but a little lacking in the creative thinking department. Seems to like taking orders.
The boss around here, or so he says. Bigger than other hobgoblins, which is probably why they listen to him.
Like a lion... from Hell. Big pointy teeth, serious claws, and fire magic.
A mobile slime mold the size of a small dog.
A large squishy with a wild tangle of hardened bits that act as antlers for fighting.
A very large squishy that actively seeks out organics to break down into food for its herd.
A human who specializes in raising and caring for squishy.
